#: src/mathlib.c:1047
#, c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"* Notice: \"%s\" was selected, but you can only change to a\n"
"* different Intel MKL threading library by restarting xnec2c.\n"
"* \n"
"* However, you may continue to select any other Linear Algebra library\n"
"* without restart, including this same Intel MKL library.  All other\n"
"* Intel MKL threading libraries are disabled until restart because of an \n"
"* MKL limitation where the MKL threading library can only be dynamically\n"
"* linked only once per runtime.\n"
"* \n"
"* See Intel's documentation on mkl_set_threading_layer() for more detail.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"* Obs: \"%s\" valdes, men du kan bara byta till ett\n"
"* annat Intel MKL-trådningsbibliotek genom att starta om xnec2c.\n"
"* \n"
"* Du kan dock fortsätta att välja vilket annat linjärt algebrabibliotek\n"
"* som helst utan omstart, inklusive samma Intel MKL-bibliotek.  Alla andra\n"
"* Intel MKL-trådningsbibliotek är inaktiverade tills omstart på grund av en\n"
"* MKL-begränsning där MKL-trådningsbiblioteket bara kan länkas dynamiskt\n"
"* en gång per körtillfälle.\n"
"* \n"
"* Se Intels dokumentation om mkl_set_threading_layer() för mer detaljer.\n"

